---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
const breadcrumbs = [
  { name: 'Home', url: '/' },
  { name: 'Service Providers', url: '/for-providers' },
  { name: 'Grooming', url: '/for-providers/grooming' }
];
---
<BaseLayout
  title="Grooming Services on BreederHQ Marketplace"
  description="List your grooming business on the BreederHQ Marketplace and get found by breeders, buyers, and owners in your area. Free to list."
  breadcrumbs={breadcrumbs}
>
<main>
  <section class="bg-gradient-to-b from-emerald-50 to-white py-20">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-4xl px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center">
      <div class="text-4xl mb-4">✂️</div>
      <h1 class="text-5xl font-bold tracking-tight text-gray-900 mb-6">Grooming Services</h1>
      <p class="text-xl text-gray-600 max-w-2xl mx-auto mb-10">
        Breed-specific groomers, show prep specialists, and coat care professionals -
        breeders, buyers, and pet owners in your area are searching for grooming services on the BreederHQ Marketplace.
      </p>
      <a href="https://accounts.breederhq.com/register?intent=provider_marketplace" class="bg-emerald-700 text-white px-8 py-4 rounded-lg text-lg font-semibold hover:bg-emerald-600">
        List Your Grooming Business
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="py-16 bg-white">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-4xl px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-8">What people search for</h2>
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
        <div class="bg-stone-50 rounded-xl p-6 border border-stone-200">
          <h3 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">From Breeders</h3>
          <ul class="text-sm text-gray-600 space-y-2">
            <li>Litter grooming before placement photos</li>
            <li>Show grooming and breed-specific trims</li>
            <li>Hand-stripping for terrier and wire-coat breeds</li>
            <li>Pre-show bathing, blow-out, and scissoring</li>
            <li>Coat maintenance for breeding stock</li>
            <li>Puppy first-groom experiences</li>
            <li>Mobile grooming for multi-animal households</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-stone-50 rounded-xl p-6 border border-stone-200">
          <h3 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">From Buyers &amp; Pet Owners</h3>
          <ul class="text-sm text-gray-600 space-y-2">
            <li>Regular breed-appropriate grooming</li>
            <li>De-shedding and coat maintenance</li>
            <li>Nail trimming and ear cleaning</li>
            <li>Medicated or sensitive-skin baths</li>
            <li>Creative grooming and styling</li>
            <li>Cat grooming and lion cuts</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="py-16 bg-stone-50">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-4xl px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-8">Why it works for groomers</h2>
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
        <div class="text-center">
          <div class="text-2xl mb-3">🔄</div>
          <h3 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">Repeat bookings</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">Grooming is recurring by nature. Every 4-8 weeks, your clients are back. Breeders with multiple animals need you even more often.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="text-center">
          <div class="text-2xl mb-3">📍</div>
          <h3 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">Local search</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">People search by location and breed expertise. If you know their breed's coat, they find you.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="text-center">
          <div class="text-2xl mb-3">⭐</div>
          <h3 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">Identity and credentials</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">Confirm your identity through Stripe Identity and list the credentials you actually hold. Registry-backed confirmations appear automatically where the issuing body maintains a public registry; everything else displays as your attestation. BreederHQ does not vouch for credentials.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="py-16 bg-white">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-4xl px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">Your listing includes</h2>
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-4">
        <div class="flex items-start gap-3 p-4 bg-stone-50 rounded-lg">
          <span class="text-emerald-600 font-bold mt-0.5">&#10003;</span>
          <span class="text-sm text-gray-700">Business profile with breed specialties, services, and availability</span>
        </div>
        <div class="flex items-start gap-3 p-4 bg-stone-50 rounded-lg">
          <span class="text-emerald-600 font-bold mt-0.5">&#10003;</span>
          <span class="text-sm text-gray-700">Coverage area and location-based discovery</span>
        </div>
        <div class="flex items-start gap-3 p-4 bg-stone-50 rounded-lg">
          <span class="text-emerald-600 font-bold mt-0.5">&#10003;</span>
          <span class="text-sm text-gray-700">Before-and-after photos of your grooming work</span>
        </div>
        <div class="flex items-start gap-3 p-4 bg-stone-50 rounded-lg">
          <span class="text-emerald-600 font-bold mt-0.5">&#10003;</span>
          <span class="text-sm text-gray-700">Flexible pricing display</span>
        </div>
        <div class="flex items-start gap-3 p-4 bg-stone-50 rounded-lg">
          <span class="text-emerald-600 font-bold mt-0.5">&#10003;</span>
          <span class="text-sm text-gray-700">Identity confirmation via Stripe Identity, registry passthrough where supported</span>
        </div>
        <div class="flex items-start gap-3 p-4 bg-stone-50 rounded-lg">
          <span class="text-emerald-600 font-bold mt-0.5">&#10003;</span>
          <span class="text-sm text-gray-700">Recommendations from your clients</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="py-16 bg-gradient-to-br from-emerald-900 to-emerald-800">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-4xl px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-4 text-white">Free</h2>
      <p class="text-sm text-emerald-200 mb-3">No commissions. Cancel anytime.</p>
      <p class="text-lg text-emerald-200 mb-8">One listing puts your grooming business in front of everyone searching for grooming services on the marketplace.</p>
      <a href="https://accounts.breederhq.com/register?intent=provider_marketplace" class="bg-white text-emerald-800 px-8 py-4 rounded-lg text-lg font-semibold hover:bg-emerald-50">
        List Your Grooming Business
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>
</main>
</BaseLayout>
